<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5690] Null pointerException in AbstractStatsValues.accumulate</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5690</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It happens when there is a string field with docValues=&quot;true&quot; and default=&quot;&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
Then, with documents that have empty string value in the field,&lt;br/&gt;
values.exists(docID) is true but values.strVal(docID) is null, and it throws null pointer exception when trying to add the value to distinctValues set.&lt;br/&gt;
the solr query is stats=true&amp;amp;stats.field=X&amp;amp;stats.calcdistinct=true&lt;/p&gt;

